{"tid":2371094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多州首府現武裝示威者，持槍黑人闖國會被捕","createTime":"2021-01-18T14:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T14:11:40.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee305c7129be2fe4bae93094023543f5a11c8df9","tid":2371094,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普任內最後一個周日（17日），俄亥俄州、猶他州、德州、俄勒岡州、新罕布什爾州及密歇根州首府有人持槍示威；雖然人數及規模不及預期，但警方仍嚴陣以待。首都華盛頓警方於同日凌晨，在國會附近拘捕一名特朗普支持者，搜出一枝Glock22手槍、3個大容量彈匣及37發子彈。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的22歲黑人男子貝里（Guy Berry）來自維珍尼亞州戈登斯維爾（Gordonsville），周日凌晨在麻薩諸塞大道行走時，裝有手槍的槍套清晰可見。他其後在一個檢查站遇上警員截查，搜出手槍、彈匣及子彈而被捕，被控無牌攜帶手槍、擁有大容量供彈裝置及未經登記的彈藥。<br />\n貝里於2017年在維珍尼亞州夏洛茨維爾，涉嫌在距離學校不足1,000米外開槍被捕，最終撤銷控罪，但導致他無法參軍，只能以駕駛貨車維生。親人曾勸貝里注意黑人身份，不要公開持槍，但他不相信。除了貝里外，國會警察於上周五（15日）亦拘捕一名涉嫌持偽冒通行證的維珍尼亞州男子，搜出手槍及超過500發子彈。<br />\n<br />\n此外，國會警察於上周六（16日）早上在哥倫布圓環附近拘捕一名女子，指她涉嫌偽冒執法人員、不服從及企圖逃走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210118/bkn-20210118063504807-0118_00992_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210118%2Fbkn-20210118063504807-0118_00992_001.html&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=19c2ad7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210118/bkn-20210118063504807-0118_00992_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"27e3a4e064ade1412a47127febc99296c046b27c","tid":2371094,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"內戰了。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64804ea29b59bb5a94db153139b4df8107fe6ab","tid":2371094,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"侵侵贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fdeda06275ab5707cd5893d563c1e1c658cc24","tid":2371094,"uid":86246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"點解可以拉黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />racist"},{"pid":"ae191b3db3585466a502db8671f0bb5d49b408de","tid":2371094,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fdeda06275ab5707cd5893d563c1e1c658cc24","tid":2371094,"uid":86246,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"點解可以拉黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />racist"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"希望牙登牙麗即刻釋放所有黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d850c0488c9496ef77ddeb761d77b1154e4b590","tid":2371094,"uid":125110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"BLM！點可以拉黑人"}]}